        <h3>레이어 선택 안내<br>Layer Selection Guide</h3>
<p>
    좌측 <img src="https://st3.depositphotos.com/4562487/13400/v/1600/depositphotos_134003474-stock-illustration-loading-data-icon-illustration.jpg" alt="레이어 선택 아이콘" width="20" height="20"> 을 누르시면 장소 종류별 레이어 선택이 가능합니다!<br>
    Click the <img src="path-to-your-image.png" alt="Layer Selection Icon" width="20" height="20"> icon on the left to select layers for different types of places!
